# --- Infra/deploy creds (used by `alchemy deploy`; NEVER bound to the Worker) ---
# Cloudflare account to deploy to. Required when your creds can see more than one
# account, otherwise Alchemy picks one arbitrarily. The creds must have access to it.
CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=
ALCHEMY_STATE_TOKEN=
ALCHEMY_STAGE=prod

# This app has no runtime secrets. If you add one, follow the pattern in
# docs/secrets.md (add it here, to [secrets] required in wrangler.toml, and as an
# alchemy.secret.env binding in alchemy.run.ts — plus ALCHEMY_PASSWORD above).
